title: Buettner drives in six as Golden Eagles win eighth straight - Tennessee Tech
content: Buettner drives in six as Golden Eagles win eighth straight  Tennessee Tech
description:
COOKEVILLE, Tenn. â€“ With the way Abby Buettner was hitting over the last four days, the Tennessee Tech designated player might not have wanted the Golden Eagle Classic to end.

Buettner hit two home runs against Indiana State and had six RBI on Monday to lead the Golden Eagles to an 11-3 win over Bellarmine and a 7-4 win over the Sycamores to close out the event. Buettner finished the tournament hitting .462 with four home runs and 11 RBI.
